Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.26,0:01:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四話 熱血的馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好,亞加瑪就這樣往後退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要活埋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?奇馬達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.44,0:02:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還算沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算把船身掩護起來了\N奇馬達先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.87,0:02:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請再輕搖船身兩三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.64,0:02:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣才藏的完美阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輕搖嗎?辦的到嗎,凱撒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.81,0:02:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要輕搖一點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又不是搖酒的酒保...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼快就離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.60,0:03:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要使用信用卡支付嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.33,0:03:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉,我沒有卡,也沒有現金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用這個付帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安,馬士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.59,0:03:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨夜在垃圾推山中徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去視察殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.83,0:03:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這打扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經妨礙了我的任務阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪可能換地點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去偵查了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.78,0:03:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊員都派去偵查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會遵守大人你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡可能不流一滴血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而得到亞加瑪的命令的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.36,0:04:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想請你看一個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我去看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要花你一點時間了\N沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.89,0:04:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不流一滴血\N就能得到亞加瑪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.43,0:04:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是最好的\N然後在視察殖民地的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.21,0:04:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哈曼大人統治地球時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.81,0:04:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟從沙比家\N即被選出來的人們阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.01,0:04:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們化成我的眼去觀察地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們化成我的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓地球成為沙比家的\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.64,0:04:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很期待你喔\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.42,0:04:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以歷史最久的第一殖民地\N香格里拉就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.77,0:05:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去那裏偵查設立我們的據點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.23,0:05:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命\N我一定不辜負你的期待,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪個笨蛋開的車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連交通訊號都不會看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不看紅綠燈的人是你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,現在不是玩的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫我大叔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無理的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.95,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,教育那些小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶給他們夢想是我們的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活潑的小孩是最好的戰力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安,還有牛奶嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.96,0:05:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安,莉娜,我有幫你留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,三天沒來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還要上學,真是辛苦阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.13,0:05:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近怎麼一下子就賣光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.39,0:06:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,因為貨物都被\N掉去港口跟十町目的醫院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十町目?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.86,0:06:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安\N早安,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們又不去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐完工作我們就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.44,0:06:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騙人,你們別去找我哥哥阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.61,0:06:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,起來阿\N知道亞加瑪在哪裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.23,0:06:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快穿上衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫人趕快的是你們阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在拖拉下去\N亞加瑪會逃掉的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,別一直大喊亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被別人聽到怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.84,0:06:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你害我們被罵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.61,0:06:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的!是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.08,0:06:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.75,0:06:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了,她來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.02,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去亞加瑪對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.69,0:06:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉查出亞加瑪在垃圾場阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以去阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,開車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.07,0:07:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把MS當禮物拿回來給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,我得想各辦法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許可以找花小姐商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家醫院?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼髒的地方會有什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的傷兵住進那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.44,0:07:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經答應捐款給醫院\N所以利用這關係...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把傷兵拿來當人質嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.56,0:07:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是人質,是盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以這樣,快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准採取卑鄙手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.98,0:07:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.54,0:08:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多溫柔阿,挺身保護病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.24,0:08:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他等於是白衣天使阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有沒有受傷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.78,0:08:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼我幫的上忙的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我還得照顧這患者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不能走嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.87,0:08:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘉美尤能走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.58,0:08:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只是因為戰爭而失去神智
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.96,0:08:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是戰爭的犧牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了,護士小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是護士小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.57,0:08:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是你的兄弟嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.66,0:08:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是男朋友阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.05,0:08:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到這地方有你這麼好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的人一定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對人保持應有的距離
