Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把小孩帶到艦橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易把Z高達偷出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能就這樣被打壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙門關起來,變成螢幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.73,0:18:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害,是360度螢幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你若以為這樣就能打倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太差勁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.72,0:18:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想逃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易偷到,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以讓他受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃跑太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你該堂堂正正來決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不想保護自己的船嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.81,0:18:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.86,0:18:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用來福槍會傷害到一般民眾\N可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩死了,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.98,0:19:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迫不得已,戈圖,用陷阱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要使用嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.23,0:19:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在引誘他過去,你準備陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.41,0:19:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.72,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然違反騎士精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是為了糾正社會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺悟吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上當了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.92,0:19:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人,艙門沒關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼,關起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在宇宙對打嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.33,0:20:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按下自動平衡按鈕,在右邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的用你的操縱桿來操縱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辦的到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被躲過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要用這個狀態打嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜下來,你辦的到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.05,0:20:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?紅色燈亮了,空氣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空氣外洩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.69,0:20:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能讓Z高達受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,密達斯呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是經由港口出去很花時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.01,0:20:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就從同一個破洞出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會一直挨打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次是你運氣好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為你能打贏我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子我要改變未來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.62,0:20:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,氧氣不夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.25,0:20:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起來阿,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,還有死前掙扎嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.25,0:21:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會死的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.14,0:21:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏了!打贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他打贏了,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.83,0:21:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的\N好,我們現在去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你留在原地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要拿回Z剛達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.67,0:21:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,我又做白工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會請你吃ㄧ頓早餐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後乖乖回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.77,0:21:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想因為氧氣不足而死嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.87,0:21:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在就走陷阱的洞回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.63,0:21:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是洞開始合起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.29,0:21:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?那快阻止阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.69,0:21:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,你這個笨蛋東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是這樣,我才會被打敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,快點吧,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.59,0:21:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.21,0:22:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.60,0:22:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個天使..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.07,0:22:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要停下來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.88,0:22:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邪念會帶來失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.90,0:22:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人\N我一定創造出你要的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.63,0:23:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓋蒙這個人 在收破爛的同行裏評價很不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.95,0:23:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他成為了馬士文的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.03,0:23:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花也因為卡繆沒有精神而沒有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.17,0:23:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果 只好讓我出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.98,0:24:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 Z的狀態又不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.63,0:24:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還真是煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.08,0:24:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.45,0:24:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度的決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈 好像很厲害呢

